1. create gradle project with kotlin
build.gradle
implementation "org.jetbrains.kotlinx:kotlinx-coroutines-core:1.1.1"

2. Hello.kt
import kotlinx.coroutines.GlobalScope
import kotlinx.coroutines.delay
import kotlinx.coroutines.launch

fun main(){
    GlobalScope.launch {
        delay(3000)
        println("hello")
    }
    println("there")
    Thread.sleep(5000)
}

3. Project Settings - Artifacts - '+' - jar with dependencies - main class HelloKt
   - Apply - Ok - Build - Build Artifacts - build 
    output to out/artifacts/del3_jar/del3.jar

4. run it with java
    java -cp .:del3.jar HelloKt
